data.description: Outstanding opportunity to finish out this nice basement rancher with an acre plus flat yard with creek. List price includes a lender approved escrow hold-back of $25.000 so you can finish this home without having to do a renovation loan.  Seller's have done the heavy lifting for you including a new HVAC. All you need to do is finish the sheet-rock, and pick out your paint and flooring. Contractor estimates are available. Need more space? The basement has been roughed in and would make a great extra living area for Mom, Dad or who ever. Fenced in dog area in the back and there is a relaxing creek at the bottom of the property. Don't let this opportunity slip by! Make an appointment to see this today.
